{"tid":1780633,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"庭上灑淚談肛交 歌手稱是第一次","createTime":"2019-12-12T13:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T06:12:35.000Z","uid":1426,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"48187475bb08bd32489c06398259c5f471c1abcc","tid":1780633,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20130911/large/1378891763_7daa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20130911%2Flarge%2F1378891763_7daa.jpg&h=aba13b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告梁柏廷（右二）與盧海鵬合照。<br />\n<br />\n年青歌手梁柏廷（Jero）被控用肛交片段勒索男同志案，梁下午繼續出庭自辯，他否認勒索之餘反指實是遭事主雞姦，更在庭上流下男兒淚，指自己是第一次跟男人肛交，當日感到痛楚，他認為自己還年幼，「原本打算大個啲先諗性的事」，法庭更一度要休庭讓他平伏心情。<br />\n<br />\n現年21歲的梁柏廷，指當日遭事主雞姦後認為對方要負責任，於是向對方借錢，又指由於當時他剛簽下唱片公司並已拍好唱片封套，有自己的歌迷會及歌迷專業、曾與盧海鵬同台演出、獲楊受成胞弟聘請到其酒吧演出等，有感事業剛起步，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以免被傳媒知道自己是同性戀者</span>，所以未有報警。"},{"pid":"52ba24db4ba8a9ef3272cacb03b8e05d5735f9f0","tid":1780633,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"以為係麻友第一次肛交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a130dee55028e9b44a91b4390c5c4112e00cc24","tid":1780633,"uid":234553,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:54:29.000Z","msg":"指自己是第一次跟男人肛交，當日感到痛楚，他認為自己還年幼，「原本打算大個啲先諗性的事」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac27871329a76c822867d0ecbcb5cf814cca91d4","tid":1780633,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf207d010a62d5702a6b20ff4732c12df5ce5f3","tid":1780633,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"52ba24db4ba8a9ef3272cacb03b8e05d5735f9f0","tid":1780633,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-